''' Ede North/Ede South/Egbedore/Ejigbo''' is a [[National Assembly of Nigeria|National Assembly]] constituency in [[Osun State]]. The constituency has been represented by [[Falade Ajibade]] since 2007.

It covers the [[Local Government Areas of Nigeria|Local Government Areas]] of [[Ede South]], [[Ede North]], [[Egbedore]] and [[Ejigbo]].

